target: There are many trains to your destination what time would you like to leave?
context: <user> I need a cheap place to stay, what would you recommend? <system> I have about 10 different options. Do you prefer a hotel or guesthouse? <user> It doesnt matter. I need free parking and prefer a place with 4 stars. <system> The Alexander Bed and Breakfast is in the centre of town, has 4 stars, is cheap, and has free parking and internet. Would this work for you? <user> Yes, this will work for me. Please send me the address, postcode and reference number. <system> Absolutely. The Address is: 56 saint barnabas road cb12de and I can give you the reference number after we book it. <user> What type of hotel is this? <system> It is a guesthouse.<user> And what type of hotel is that? <system> A guesthouse is a type of hotel, thus it is a guesthouse type.<user> I'd like some information on a train next. <system> Where will you be departing from?<user> I will be departing from Kings Lynn, and traveling to Cambridge. <system>
